data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in the premier community of Leeland Station! Stand out features include GREAT Location, Large Flat Lot, In Ground POOL, and Energy Efficient!! This 4 bedroom (4th bedroom in basement NTC) & 3.5-bathroom property is a true gem that has everything you've been searching for in a home. As you step inside, you'll notice the beautiful LVP flooring throughout. The spacious kitchen is open to the large family room with a beautiful gas fireplace, a separate formal dining room, and a formal living room. Perfect space to create a playroom or office. Upper level offers three bedrooms, each generously sized and thoughtfully designed. The primary suite is a true retreat with two spacious closets, a sitting room, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. The unfinished basement is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. With its generous space for entertaining and a large wet bar, it's the ideal place to create your dream recreation room or home theater. Step outside into your own private oasis, where the entertainment possibilities are endless. The expansive backyard boasts a sizable deck, perfect for entertaining and those summer BBQs. But the real showstopper is the in-ground pool with its concrete patio surround, promising countless hours of fun and relaxation under the sun!! Located within walking distance to the VRE Station, shopping and restaurants, this home offers a lifestyle of convenience and luxury that you won't find elsewhere. Come check out this entertainer's delight before it's GONE!
